    "body": "Problem: nightly builds were always compared against HEAD, causing false outdated warnings.\r\n\r\nSolution: fetch both HEAD and refs/tags/nightly, match local commit against nightly first, fall back to HEAD if no match.\r\n\r\nFix #38141\r\n\r\n\r\nOutdate Nightly:\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1918\" height=\"452\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/479e2623-6ae3-43cb-907a-22d89e342309\" />\r\n\r\n\r\nLatest Nightly:\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1642\" height=\"480\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/fd45e55a-b5a8-4ab7-ba0c-076e3b5a5403\" />\r\n\r\n",
    "closed_at": "2026-03-06T07:58:42Z",
